<lyrics>[V1]
 tóng shēng zhǎng zài měi lì de tǔ de shàng gòng tóng yōng yǒu yī gè lán tiān
 kě wàng zhēn zhèng de zì yóu yǔ hé píng méi yǒu zhēng zhàn dōu fàng xià qiāng gān
 yuàn shén de ér nǚ bù zài shòu kǔ shòu nán yuàn shén de pū rén dōu píng píng ān
 wú lùn dào hé de zài méi yǒu suǒ liàn fú yīn zǎo rì chuán biàn
 shén a yuàn nǐ jiù tā bǎo shǒu tā men píng píng ān ān
 shén a yuàn nǐ jiù tā bǎo shǒu tā men píng píng ān ān.</lyrics>
<title>yuàn shén de pū rén dōu píng píng ān ān 迦南217</title>
